<p><em>J curled into a far tighter ball, disgustingly effeminate fingernails digging into their disgustingly calloused palms, but even so, they wouldn't cry. God hated <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">men</span> who couldn't stand up to their own problems.</em></p>
